\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {S5}{\ignorespaces Quiet-window robustness scan: fitted enrollment-time frailty variance \(\hat {\mittheta }_{0,d}\) vs.\nobreakspace  {}quiet-window midpoint date for the Czech 2021--2024 enrollment cohort, using 12-month windows shifted monthly from April 2022 through April 2023. Marker shape denotes birth decade (1940s, 1950s). Filled markers indicate diagnostic pass; open markers indicate diagnostic failure. The figure is intended as a technical stability scan of the estimator rather than as substantive evidence for any one cohort narrative.}}{60}{figure.5}\protected@file@percent }
